title: Trump Speech, Steve's Diet, The Wall, Kells Investigation, New Year Goals, Obama Ave., Jimmy Kimmel, Closing Remarks and more.
itunes:title: Trump Speech, Steve's Diet, The Wall, Kells Investigation, New Year Goals, Obama Ave., Jimmy Kimmel, Closing Remarks and more.
description:
Trump does his nine minute speech to the nation. Steve has his special diet that he has been sticking to. The Wall that Trump is talking about just has people shaking their heads. The docuseries about R. Kelly is now leading to investigations. All bad for Kells! The CEO continues to talk about his 2019 goals. Trump Tower maybe located on Obama Avenue because of a petition to honor the last President. Jimmy Kimmel is offering help to federal employees. Today in Closing Remarks, Big Dog talks about expecting great things and how beneficial it really is and more.
